{"tid":1382140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"\"雙非媽媽\": 「不會白占香港福利，大不了多來消費! 」","createTime":"2019-07-29T11:49:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T13:25:13.000Z","uid":226548,"like":2,"dislike":102,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"b622edf864de0bf137d32aa81ba655ffc81b0d6a","tid":1382140,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:49:00.000Z","msg":"「雙非媽媽」：為了省20萬的超生罰款，<br />\n我把孩子生在了香港<br />\nSoure: <a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/71641033\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzhuanlan.zhihu.com%2Fp%2F71641033&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiiTyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=7742f0a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/71641033</a><br />\n<br />\n01.<br />\n我叫詹瀟瀟，我是一名「雙非媽媽」。<br />\n<br />\n所謂「雙非」，就是說父母雙非都非香港身份，而孩子出生在香港，按照香港的法律，只要在香港出生，就是香港人了。<strong>2012年，<span style=\"color: red;\">為了省20萬的超生罰款</span>，我們一家決定，把二寶生在了香港。從此之後，我的孩子，就成了「雙非兒童」。</strong><br />\n<br />\n其實在我們之前，去香港生孩子已經成為了一種潮流，尤其是像我們這樣在深圳居住的人，過關是很方便的。我之前看到地鐵上一個個小朋友背着大大的書包，去福田口岸過關，再坐大巴去香港上學，覺得很心疼：那麼小的孩子，每天上學花在路上的時間都兩三個小時了，而且他們去香港之後，會不會被當地的小朋友歧視呢？<br />\n<br />\n這種擔心，沒想到後來卻成為了現實。<br />\n<br />\n這時一位姐妹對我說：「你為什麼不去香港生呢？」「香港生？」我愣了一下，腦海里想起之前在地鐵上看到的「雙非兒童」，心中糾結起來：「那以後孩子去香港上學會不會很麻煩？」姐妹說：「其實也不麻煩的，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">拿了香港身份多好啊，什麼撫養費一分都不用交</span></strong>，那邊最差的幼兒園都比這裏好，以後申請外國的學校都容易，你不是一直想送孩子去留學嗎？」看我沉默了一下，姐妹說：「是不是覺得很值？」回到家裏，把這個想法跟老公說了，權衡利弊之後，我們做出了決定。<br />\n<br />\n從那個時候起，一些香港人對內地來的孕婦就比較反感了，在香港待產的時候，就能感覺到周圍人看我們的目光有所不同，但政府的法律還沒有修改，所以，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">即便有幾個香港人不滿，他們也不能把我趕走。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n當時我心裏就想：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我們不會白占你們香港的福利，大不了我以後多來香港消費就是，我孩子長大後，說不定還在香港工作納稅呢。</span></span></strong>不管怎樣，這個孩子我是在香港生定了。"},{"pid":"554025d923209e76b85caaf2d0e8d847602b3c47","tid":1382140,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":32,"score":-32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:50:25.000Z","msg":"02<br />\n<br />\n除了辛苦，還要面對「雙非家庭」特有的苦惱，也就是我當初的擔心成了真。<br />\n<br />\n一天二寶告訴我，他不想去上學了。我以為是他偷懶了，沒理他，拉着他繼續往關口走。他哇的一聲哭了出來，甩開我的手，蹲在地上再也不肯往關口挪一步。他向我哭訴：有同學嘲笑他，不跟他玩，說他是「小蝗蟲」。<br />\n<br />\n我沒有想到這樣的遭遇會發生在我的孩子身上，看着委屈的兒子，我很堅定地告訴他：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">只有生活在底層的香港人才會說別人是蝗蟲</span>，因為他們沒本事賺錢，要靠政府幫他們，他們沒有禮貌，我們不要因為沒有禮貌的人生氣」。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n「媽媽，做香港人真的那麼好嗎？」兒子瞪着一雙好奇、不解的淚眼望着我，我竟一時語塞。"},{"pid":"aac3ac26f414aabcdbe5f321b19597707ad3fb2c","tid":1382140,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":31,"score":-31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:51:49.000Z","msg":"03.<br />\n<br />\n但任何事情都是要付出代價的。有人說我們這些「雙非家庭」，是兩頭佔便宜，可誰又知道，兩頭的便宜不好占，兩頭的氣反倒是都要受。<br />\n<br />\n後來我跟老公商量，要不讓二寶回深圳讀國際學校吧？貴就貴了點，但這樣一來大家都不用那麼累。但老公為難地說：「<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">好不容易申請到了香港學校，放棄太可惜了。</span></strong>」<br />\n<br />\n是的，我後悔了，我後悔把孩子生在香港，他既不能融入香港，又不能回歸內地，如今，我的孩子依然在香港上學，據說「雙非兒童」有20多萬，我不知道這20多萬的家庭，有多少後悔，多少慶幸。<br />\n<br />\n世上沒有後悔藥，我只能儘自己的努力，把最好的教育資源給到孩子，也<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">希望不管是大陸還是香港，都能夠對「雙非兒童」更加友善和包容。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n口述：詹瀟瀟<br />\n<br />\n整理：Mr海"},{"pid":"1b697c70812cd8ca1627ab3d28cbdec28fb220bd","tid":1382140,"uid":275370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:51:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b817335700fc8b29dc2c34b2a02f5ff32c338c4e","tid":1382140,"uid":235015,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:52:26.000Z","msg":"上一秒話想慳錢，冇錢<br />\n<br />\n下一秒就話消費<br />\n<br />\n咁有錢你上邊交罰款咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd3bc86514874f186efcb37fff443cf2462c6b66","tid":1382140,"uid":10323,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:52:53.000Z","msg":"死開啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b584543c5ec752c5fd504eecf8a717afab693d0a","tid":1382140,"uid":245033,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:53:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">包容</span></span>呢2個字有時真係難聽過粗口"},{"pid":"6d291b151a2996d4f24b248e4c180b13113d94c0","tid":1382140,"uid":88967,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:53:45.000Z","msg":"包容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 死返去你個國家喇蝗蟲"},{"pid":"25fef4ed3ae563f4cc11e8b37fb24c0ae817d404","tid":1382140,"uid":269694,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:57:10.000Z","msg":"屌，佢所做嘅嘢咪係拎咁香港福利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5ce46e6f48bc9e1763e317994756863078a097d","tid":1382140,"uid":70417,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:57:57.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">蝗蟲</span></strong><br />\n利申 35k窮撚"},{"pid":"e0c64c73d2ac29475aaa461b31f695e9f28954ad","tid":1382140,"uid":78769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:58:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">包容</span></span>呢2個字有時真係難聽過粗口</blockquote><br />\n哦，翻譯問題，轉返我哋嘅語言係啞忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bd18278f830ba3bab3dbd225344c982b25687e3","tid":1382140,"uid":59919,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b817335700fc8b29dc2c34b2a02f5ff32c338c4e","tid":1382140,"uid":235015,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:52:26.000Z","msg":"上一秒話想慳錢，冇錢<br />\n<br />\n下一秒就話消費<br />\n<br />\n咁有錢你上邊交罰款咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:58:29.000Z","msg":"罰款白交<br />\n買野佢自己用得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a79e48bd826b754983201a6fcb13c585f1036a75","tid":1382140,"uid":137921,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:58:50.000Z","msg":"我不會白占香港福利<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由你決定一落黎生個下已經係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a800316b5534fbb7782404888cddab840d9d4cd","tid":1382140,"uid":34616,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:59:00.000Z","msg":"躝啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"5113c1208907f1399e23c9b88a5219fc59c8f15b","tid":1382140,"uid":191504,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:59:19.000Z","msg":"呢種咪蝗蟲mentality囉<br />\n凡事都有代價架啦<br />\n成日諗住痴着數<br />\n最後發現有downside就淨係識得怪人<br />\n講到全世界欠咗佢咁<br />\n黨叫你生一個咪生一個算囉<br />\n唔聽話懶醒撞板怪得邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0eed5559da10c8d0b07d2abfae6e4ba28e56389","tid":1382140,"uid":264067,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:59:57.000Z","msg":"屌，go back to your fucking China <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f02f71e0ac3a0a1c9caf67c938150c92ae42077","tid":1382140,"uid":274658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:00:25.000Z","msg":"土共代表<br />\n一貫答法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88218096fedc7f331c840c3acc96ab6d031987d9","tid":1382140,"uid":157138,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:00:56.000Z","msg":"20萬都唔捨得俾，又話多消費仲要去埋外國留學？新疆留學啊？"},{"pid":"1d7bd5cb7e00d5412d0bb07f2e8547faa8a8ef36","tid":1382140,"uid":78769,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:01:56.000Z","msg":"係咪連粵語都唔（識）講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實由細到大讀者，預過新移民唔出奇，我都預過，但唔覺得同本地出世嘅有咩分別，如果連粵語都唔識講，咁喺文化定義上都唔叫香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP.s. 阿媽係大陸廣東人，自己土生土長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ce7f6e2309cdd64510e06346551f7d762b5963","tid":1382140,"uid":198481,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:03:06.000Z","msg":"消你老母個費！<br />\n憎撚到依種蝗婦入骨，乜撚到搶！<br />\n賤種！"},{"pid":"22716a20e8604f4d1def699619c8f81c1af84ac0","tid":1382140,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:03:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪連粵語都唔（識）講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實由細到大讀書，遇過新移民唔出奇，我都遇過，但唔覺得同本地出世嘅有咩分別，如果連粵語都唔識講，咁喺文化定義上都唔叫香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP.s. 阿媽係大陸廣東人，自己土生土長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0b5f552bd0f1cffacae662b2d77053789a4e1654","tid":1382140,"uid":213142,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:03:52.000Z","msg":"又要做雞，又要拎貞節牌坊就係呢啲"},{"pid":"498e90d87e8e83d11b4ac25044a4526263c5bb7f","tid":1382140,"uid":260367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:04:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c01ae1fd8a0135164f101caaa31ab056ff80e32a","tid":1382140,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:05:17.000Z","msg":"香港要改變犯罪之都之名，要取消雙非永久居民資格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成班友超生咪犯法囉"},{"pid":"93c33d55e28de6c93cbf870fc04a321255f6b349","tid":1382140,"uid":73340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:10:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />叫中國政府包容你咪得囉<br />\n做咩要叫香港包容呢"}]}